# Documentation

## Read first
`PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` — permanent project memory

## Update when applicable (same session)
| File | When |
|------|------|
| `CHANGELOG.md` | Any user-visible or behavioral change |
| `HEALTH.md` | Dimension scores shift ≥ 1 point |
| `TECH_DEBT.md` | New debt found or item resolved |
| `IDEAS.md` | New ideas only — never implement without approval |
| `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` | Schema, API, business rules, or architecture change |

## Changelog entry format
```
## [version] — Title
### Changed / Added / Fixed / Removed
### Files
### Breaking changes
### Migration
### Testing performed
### Known limitations
```

## Do not create unsolicited docs
No new README sections or guides unless user asks or release requires it.

## Session end (mandatory)
Exactly **5 ranked improvements** with: priority, effort, business value, technical value, risk, files affected. **Do not implement without approval.**
